article_id:929,category_name:News,title_name:Limited-Time Void Battle Endeavors, Now Live!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b0970642e344d8f74b4e34bc7220e779.png,message:<div>Limited Void Battle Endeavors are available between <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1576476000"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1577771999"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>We have also adjusted the drop rewards for Void Battles and adjusted the balance for certain weapons.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b0970642e344d8f74b4e34bc7220e779.png"></div><div>A call for help came from a neighboring city, reporting attacks by ferocious fiends and dragons that had been transformed by black mana! Now it&#39;s up to the Prince and his companions to save the city in peril!</div><div><br></div><div>■Void Battles Treasure Trade</div><div>Twinkling Sand will be added to the Treasure Trade for Void Battles.</div><div>Note: The exchange limit will refresh on the last day of the month at 10:00 PM PT.</div><div><br></div><div>■Void Battles Schedule</div><div>You can play Void Battles anytime, regardless of the day of the week. However, the Void enemies that appear will differ based on the day. Check out the Void Battles Schedule notification for information about when each Void enemy is scheduled to appear.</div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/19999">Void Battles Schedule</a></div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time Endeavors</div><div>We&#39;re adding Limited-Time Void Battle Endeavors, separated into Daily and Limited variations.</div><div>You can complete the endeavors to obtain various rewards.</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited Void Battle Endeavors Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1576476000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1577771999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Drop Reward Adjustments and Balance Adjustments to Certain Weapons</div><div>Adjustments to the drop rewards for Void Battles and balance adjustments to certain weapons are being applied at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1576474200"></span>.</div><div>For more information, see <a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/927">＜Regarding Void Battles Drop Reward Adjustments and Balance Adjustments to Certain Weapons＞</a> notification.</div><div><br></div><div>■New Weapons You Can Craft Using Materials Obtained From Volcanic Chimera</div><div>Powerful new weapons will be added to the Void weapon series lineup under Crafting starting <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1577340000"></span>.</div><div>You must first have obtained specific weapons before you can craft weapons using materials obtained from Volcanic Chimera.</div><div>The required weapons are the flame-attuned 5★ weapons which can be crafted using materials obtained from the Smoldering Manticore.</div><div><br></div><div>The weapon that is required differs based on the weapon type for the weapon you wish to craft. You can check the requirements by selecting Materials for the Volcanic Chimera weapons on the Craft tab under Crafting.</div><div>Note: Weapons crafted using materials obtained from Volcanic Chimera cannot be dismantled.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about Void Battles, tap Events on the main page, then go to the Void Battles page and select Help.</div><div>2. For more information about Void enemies, tap Events on the main page, then go to the Void Battles page and check Details on the various quest pages.</div><div>3. You can check the Endeavors added for a limited time by tapping Endeavors on the main page, then selecting the Daily or Limited tabs.</div><div>4. Players must have completed up to Chapter 7 / 5-6 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to participate in Void Battles.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div>,start_time:1576476000,update_time1575603574